Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢美丽的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为『美』才是至上的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnDFLiSong-Bd\fs24\b0}{\fad(400,0)}美麗而殘酷的詩人\N 美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师您的确很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与您相比…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不只是外表哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体育中不是也有美丽的姿势吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一举一动　谈吐言行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.21,0:00:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心也是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为世界是可以分成两边的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的事物和丑陋的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.91,0:00:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真头疼  我恐怕是属于丑陋这一类的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又让它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽也找薛定谔？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}薛定谔：出自薛定谔的猫<schrodinger's cat>是奥地利物理学家埃尔温·薛定谔\N试图证明量子力学在宏观条件下的不完备性而提出的一个思想实验
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要给猫送死后文  怎么送啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语言不通  叫了它也不会停下等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东碰西撞地追它  结果追到这种地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  为了追猫  从那一直追到这里来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这猫还真有毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐电车也要花2个小时的路程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特快的话  是1小时48分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还不是2小时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为你这么不严谨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才无法完成定额
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的发送率可是百分之百的 NO.1 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跟笨蛋过不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像还是有点自知之明的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饲主老奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那猫好像是对没有孩子的老夫妇养的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  也就是说他们差不多同时去世的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说不定比较幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只留下一个是很残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初二同班的美川文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊　记得是很文静的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的孩子居然会枪杀自己的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是因为那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时的积怨一口气爆发了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的是煌的女儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她枪杀了父亲对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:04:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  别说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnDFLiSong-Bd\fs21\b0}襲擊美川煌的犯人是獨生女的少女A（13）嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然作家的女儿都很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 美川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要枪杀自己父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}鸥之路  感觉还不错！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为没计划性地乱找是找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你整整3天来都在没计划性的乱追
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是我们来动脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}可以预防生活习惯病糖尿病的乌龙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}木天蓼: 木天蓼基原为狝猴桃科植物葛枣狝猴桃\N果实有毒 猫及猫科动物爱吃 易引起中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  说到猫自然不能不提木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点过于理论主义  不过是有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真苫  0923
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又没有这个世界的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  你难道想当小偷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永久性的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}止步  请确认左右方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止小偷行径
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是无奈之举啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见  所以无法手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}等…文伽  我头昏啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}要坏了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs29}真的要死啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有造成致命伤的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  你肯定看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么找薛定谔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有钱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像千秋的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时都是报告说收信人不明  然后溜之大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追了3天的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜做小偷  你还真是热心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  小姐们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的衣服是情侣装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  腹语术？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有一手的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的话  很快可以人气飙升哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他们到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星探
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星探？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水蚤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没中彩的马票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光化学烟雾（公害）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秃子的脑袋上还用梳子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼装完模型剩下的框架子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少…少看不起人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这只章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  正当防卫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　我说  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥…痛…痛…放开我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你这个…放过我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买木天蓼的钱到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊　能不能不拿我当武器使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早就一直在房间打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是中学时的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天还问我名册在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来呢  薛薛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是薛定谔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一只猫  名字还那么长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有你的年龄会增长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮差是从死者中挑选的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  保持死时的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要什么都不说啦  告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是薛定谔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不用赶它走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候连薛定谔都不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕…猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵　这下有好看的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  没想到和夫是弟弟  千代之介才是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真涩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  在下夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是野岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学时的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  要？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然  什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香  你知道美川的联系方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事  想联系她下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香和美川关系很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  觉得你是不是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.35,0:10:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,线索之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和文歌  交往过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你老实回答  告诉你也可以哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点提示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『提示』？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你知道什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢文歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和美川…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我会保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  该告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『提示』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川的联系方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在医院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教务主任打电话时说的被我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.59,0:11:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤泽综合医院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『暂时住院一阵子  联系方式也转到那边』
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师在电话里跟别人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤泽综合医院…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌拒绝掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为文歌也是喜欢他的

Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你还是有可爱的地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然怕猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买完木天蓼还有剩下的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经打开了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,间接接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么的啦  都是女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还是没出现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算木天蓼的气味会扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是有极限的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让气味充满这个镇子可是很  很…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薛定谔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0825
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  别妨碍到我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡0609
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  前面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是3天前就开始追的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让给姐姐我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还姐姐　明明长不大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不同  永远年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说永远的洗衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是洗衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年后就是nice body
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}文伽的CV植田的确是nice body
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事可说不准
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人即使长成大人也没发育的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是千秋你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  前面前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能否暂时保持不动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边有点情况啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么情况啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬树么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从医院逃出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…又怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  出了点事故
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  医院就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不能称为不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  差不多到飞行时间极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拆毁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.61,0:17:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡  解除代号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0913
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认可
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖  没事的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来喜欢猫啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是我的幸运物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动会上拿下第一名时是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出差的爸爸提早回家时是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男朋友相遇时也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想我跟他的美好时光正要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  才想长大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是  反正我已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  今天是你的幸运日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  回去了还有成堆的悔过书要写哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄信人生前居住的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这间房的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才到坐电车也要花2个小时才能到的这里来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对老爷爷和老奶奶来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有那只猫是亲人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正那机器到明天才能动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就好好地告别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽  你的家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他们『结束』了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能找到这呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次事件后  三年都未曾睁开眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『未曾睁开眼』？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…到底是谁啊

